---
title: South Indian Fish & Cauliflower Curry with Garlic Rice & Cucumber Raita
description: Flaky John Dory and tender cauliflower simmer in a rich South Indian-style curry, packed with bold spices and coconutty goodness. Served with fragrant garlic rice and cooling cucumber raita, it’s a feast of flavours in every bite!
